text:
Photonics are hot too. But, I didn't put the Photonics in my bucket yet because it is not my speciality.
I am happy to have my close Silicon Valley Ph.D. friends to you to share their in-depth visions. 
@PhotonCap Ph.D. has shared his views about photonics.
@damnang2 Ph.D. provided his insight about the photonics, in addition to your $NOK question, https://t.co/vxDXFtod6T

